{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "sop", "icon": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1/LYNX_logo.svg", "internal": "LYNX_fabric_color", "version": "1.1", "namespace": "LYNX"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["LYNX Fabric Color"], "extent": [57, 79]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["With this node you can set the color of your curves. Optionally you also can set any vector or float attribute including ", {"type": "code", "text": ["width"]}, " and ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Alpha"]}, ". Use this to add textures, attribute driven colors and widths to your curves."], "extent": [79, 305]}, {"type": "vimeo_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "vimeo", "indent": 0, "text": [" Tutorial"], "role": "item", "extent": [305, 322], "body": [], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "321386151"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [343, 358], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["Features:"], "extent": [391, 401]}, {"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": ["Set and randomize any float or vector attribute including ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Cd"]}, "/", {"type": "code", "text": ["Alpha"]}, "/", {"type": "code", "text": ["width"]}, " of your input geometry."], "extent": [401, 506]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": ["Manipulate the attribute in a layer based fashion. Each layer can be one of the four types: ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_solidramp", "type": "link", "text": ["Solid/Ramp"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_solidramp", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_solidramp"}, ", ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_image", "type": "link", "text": ["Image"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_image", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_image"}, ", ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_noise", "type": "link", "text": ["Noise"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_noise", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_noise"}, " or ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection", "type": "link", "text": ["Color Correction"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection"}, " and is merged via the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mix", "type": "link", "text": ["Mix"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mix", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mix"}, " operation."], "extent": [506, 910]}], "container": true}], "attrs": {"id": "LYNX_fabric_color_overview"}}, {"level": 1, "id": "outputs", "container": true, "type": "outputs_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [910, 919], "body": [{"type": "dt_group", "body": [{"type": "dt", "indent": 0, "text": ["Output"], "extent": [919, 928], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Geometry with the manipulated attribute."], "extent": [928, 975]}], "container": true}], "container": true}], "text": "Outputs"}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [975, 987], "body": [{"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["General"], "extent": [987, 1002], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Mask"], "extent": [1002, 1009], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Mask the node effect with any point attribute, point selection or point group."], "extent": [1009, 1093]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Fiber"], "extent": [1093, 1105], "body": [{"level": 3, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Color"], "extent": [1105, 1120], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Color Attribute Name"], "extent": [1120, 1142], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Define which attribute to manipulate. It can by either a vector or float attribute. If the attribute does not exist, it will be created. Internally everything is calculated with vectors, but if the attribute is a float then it is converted via taking the luminance using the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["rgbtohsv(attribute)"]}, " function."], "extent": [1196, 1507]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_attribute_name"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Clamp Final Output Values"], "extent": [1507, 1534], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["Before writing the attribute, clamp it to the specified values."], "extent": [1534, 1603]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Edit Sets | General Settings"], "extent": [1603, 1633], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Skip: Skip this attribute edit."], "extent": [1633, 1671]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Solo: Display only this attribute edit (or all that have ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Solo"]}, " toggled on)."], "extent": [1671, 1754]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Mask: This allows you to mask the edit to a certain point group or selection. This parameter also supports expressions."], "extent": [1754, 1880], "body": [{"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "tip", "indent": 8, "role": "item", "extent": [1880, 1895], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["You can also mask it by any attribute, for example:"], "extent": [1895, 1959]}, {"lang": "vex", "type": "pre", "indent": 12, "text": ["\n            @LYNX_fabric_fiber_direction==0\n            "], "extent": [1959, 2053]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["This expression only influences curves along the horizontal axis when using this node in combination with ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_weave-1.1", "type": "link", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_weave"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_weave-1.1"}, "."], "extent": [2053, 2229]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Mode: Edits can be one of four types: ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_solidramp", "type": "link", "text": ["Solid/Ramp"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_solidramp", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_solidramp"}, ", ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_image", "type": "link", "text": ["Image"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_image", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_image"}, ", ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_noise", "type": "link", "text": ["Noise"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_noise", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_noise"}, " and ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection", "type": "link", "text": ["Color Correction"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection"}, "."], "extent": [2229, 2510]}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Mix Via: Here you set the mix method how the edit is combined with previous edits or the input attribute."], "extent": [2510, 2622], "body": [{"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "tip", "indent": 8, "role": "item", "extent": [2669, 2684], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["When using the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection", "type": "link", "text": ["Color Correction"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection"}, " mode you can choose to apply the color correction to all previous edits or only to the previous edit before it is applied to the rest of the stack. This allows you for example to remap images to a certain range before applying the image."], "extent": [2684, 3021]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mix"}}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Edit Sets | Modes"], "extent": [3021, 3040], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Solid/Ramp:"], "extent": [3082, 3100], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Color the curves along a uv attribute. Ideal for creating a base color which can be layered with later edits."], "extent": [3158, 3276]}, {"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["Base Color: The color ramp is multiplied with this Base Color."], "extent": [3276, 3349]}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["Color Remap: Control the color along the uv attribute. This is multiplied with the base color."], "extent": [3349, 3454]}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["UV Attribute: The uv attribute that drives the ramp. "], "extent": [3454, 3518], "body": [{"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "tip", "indent": 12, "role": "item", "extent": [3518, 3536], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["When using ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_weave-1.1", "type": "link", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_weave"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_weave-1.1"}, ", try using ", {"type": "code", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_uv_geo"]}, " / ", {"type": "code", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_uv_tile"]}, " / ", {"type": "code", "text": ["uv"]}, " for different effects."], "extent": [3536, 3706]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["UV Transform: Transform the uv (without actually changing the uv attribute). Use this to adjust the placement of your image."], "extent": [3706, 3841]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_solidramp"}}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Image:"], "extent": [3841, 3854], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Color the curves with an image of your choice."], "extent": [3908, 3963]}, {"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "tip", "indent": 8, "role": "item", "extent": [3963, 3977], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 12, "text": ["Images with alphas are supported. The alpha is used as an opacity map to control where the image is applied. If you want to actually influence the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Alpha"]}, " attribute, set the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_attribute_name", "type": "link", "text": ["Color Attribute Name"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_attribute_name", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_attribute_name"}, " to ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Alpha"]}, "."], "extent": [3977, 4244]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["Image: Input the image of your choice here ;)"], "extent": [4244, 4300]}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["UV Attribute: The uv attribute that drives the uv coordinates for the image. "], "extent": [4300, 4388], "body": [{"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "tip", "indent": 12, "role": "item", "extent": [4388, 4406], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["When using ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_weave-1.1", "type": "link", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_weave"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_weave-1.1"}, ", try using ", {"type": "code", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_uv_geo"]}, " / ", {"type": "code", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_uv_tile"]}, " / ", {"type": "code", "text": ["uv"]}, " for different effects."], "extent": [4406, 4576]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["Wrap: Controls how the image wraps across tiling bounds. You can let it ", {"type": "code", "text": ["repeat"]}, " / ", {"type": "code", "text": ["streak"]}, "(duplicates the edge pixel) or ", {"type": "code", "text": ["decal"]}, " (only show it in the 0-1 range)."], "extent": [4576, 4749]}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["Filter/Blur: How to filter the image. Use this to blur the image. ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Blur"]}, " controls the blur strength."], "extent": [4749, 4860], "body": [{"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "tip", "indent": 12, "role": "item", "extent": [4860, 4879], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["Try out different filters for different looks!"], "extent": [4879, 4942]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["Color Management/Gamma: If an ", {"type": "code", "text": ["OCIO"]}, " variable is set you can color transform the image via the color transforms defined by the OCIO configuration. If no variable is set you can shift the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["gamma"]}, "."], "extent": [4942, 5148]}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["UV Transform: Transform the uv (without actually changing the uv attribute). Use this to adjust the placement of your image."], "extent": [5148, 5283]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_image"}}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Noise:"], "extent": [5283, 5296], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Color the curves with noise along a uv attribute. Ideal for creating subtle color variations."], "extent": [5350, 5452]}, {"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["Type Color: Different noise types with values from 0 to 1."], "extent": [5452, 5521]}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["UV Attribute: The uv attribute that drives the ramp. "], "extent": [5521, 5585], "body": [{"type": "tip_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "tip", "indent": 12, "role": "item", "extent": [5585, 5603], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 16, "text": ["When using ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_weave-1.1", "type": "link", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_weave"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_weave-1.1"}, ", try using ", {"type": "code", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_uv_geo"]}, " / ", {"type": "code", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_uv_tile"]}, " / ", {"type": "code", "text": ["uv"]}, " for different effects."], "extent": [5603, 5773]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}], "container": true}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["Frequency/Offset/Octaves/Lacunarity/Roughness: Control your noise settings here."], "extent": [5773, 5864]}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["Color Remap: Remap the resulting noise with this ramp."], "extent": [5864, 5929]}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["UV Transform: Transform the uv (without actually changing the uv attribute). Use this to adjust the placement of your image."], "extent": [5929, 6064]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_noise"}}, {"blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "indent": 4, "text": ["Color Correction:"], "extent": [6064, 6088], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Color grade your color."], "extent": [6152, 6184]}, {"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["Randomize Seed: The name of the attribute that drives the seed when using the ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Randomize"]}, " feature for ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection_huesaturationvalue", "type": "link", "text": ["Hue/Saturation/Value"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection_huesaturationvalue", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection_huesaturationvalue"}, "."], "extent": [6184, 6391]}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["Hue/Saturation/Value: Shift the hue, change the saturation or multiply the values of your color. By enabling ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Randomize"]}, " you can randomize the actual slider value."], "extent": [6391, 6565], "body": [], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection_huesaturationvalue"}}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["Fit Range Final Value: Fit range the final output value after all color corrections have been calculated. This fit range operates unclamped."], "extent": [6652, 6803]}, {"blevel": 10, "type": "bullet", "indent": 8, "text": ["HSV Remap: Remap the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection_huesaturationvalue", "type": "link", "text": ["Hue/Saturation/Value"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection_huesaturationvalue", "fragment": "#LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection_huesaturationvalue"}, " with a ramp. This is similar to color corrections found in other DCC software packages."], "extent": [6803, 7025]}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_mode_colorcorrection"}}], "container": true}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "LYNX_fabric_color_fiber_color_id"}, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}]}], "text": "Parameters"}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [7025, 7034], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_pattern-1.1", "type": "link", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_pattern"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_pattern-1.1"}], "extent": [7034, 7098]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_weave-1.1", "type": "link", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_weave"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_weave-1.1"}], "extent": [7098, 7157]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_thread-1.1", "type": "link", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_thread"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_thread-1.1"}], "extent": [7157, 7218]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_thread_profile-1.1", "type": "link", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_thread_profile"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_thread_profile-1.1"}], "extent": [7218, 7295]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_resample-1.1", "type": "link", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_resample"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_resample-1.1"}], "extent": [7295, 7360]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_width-1.1", "type": "link", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_width"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_width-1.1"}], "extent": [7360, 7419]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1", "type": "link", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_color"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_color-1.1"}], "extent": [7419, 7478]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_convert-1.1", "type": "link", "text": ["LYNX_fabric_convert"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/LYNX--LYNX_fabric_convert-1.1"}], "extent": [7478, 7542]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["LYNX Fabric Color"], "summary": ["With this node you can set the color of your curves. Optionally you also can set any vector or float attribute including ", {"type": "code", "text": ["width"]}, " and ", {"type": "code", "text": ["Alpha"]}, ". Use this to add textures, attribute driven colors and widths to your curves."]}